  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Written Confirmed Consent,

          -  All patients meet the DSM IV criteria for generalized social anxiety disorder,

          -  A score â‰¥ 60 on the LSAS,

          -  male and female aged between 18 and 65 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Presence of any primary axis I diagnosis other than social anxiety disorder according
             to DSM-IV,

          -  alcohol and/or substance abuse according to DSM-IV criteria within the last 12 months,

          -  any personality disorder as the primary diagnosis, with the exception of avoidant
             personality disorder,

          -  patients at risk of suicide
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
